analysis.title: Global Market Outlook
analysis.content: STABLE NEUTRALITY AMIDST STRATEGIC HARD ASSET ROTATION. The GMS print of 48 dictates a neutral posture as the fiscal-monetary nexus stabilizes within Phase 2 transition weights. While credit spread compression in the HY sector suggests resilient solvency, the flat OGV vector and 1.77% real interest rate preclude aggressive equity expansion. Capital flows prioritize commodity convexityevidenced by copper and gold appreciationoffsetting crypto-sentiment degradation. Tactical patience is required until regime acceleration clears the 55-threshold. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]

reports.EN: STABLE NEUTRALITY AMIDST STRATEGIC HARD ASSET ROTATION. The GMS print of 48 dictates a neutral posture as the fiscal-monetary nexus stabilizes within Phase 2 transition weights. While credit spread compression in the HY sector suggests resilient solvency, the flat OGV vector and 1.77% real interest rate preclude aggressive equity expansion. Capital flows prioritize commodity convexityevidenced by copper and gold appreciationoffsetting crypto-sentiment degradation. Tactical patience is required until regime acceleration clears the 55-threshold. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
reports.ES: NEUTRALIDAD ESTABLE ANTE ROTACIN ESTRATGICA DE ACTIVOS. El GMS de 48 dicta una postura neutral mientras el nexo fiscal-monetario se estabiliza en la Fase 2. Aunque la compresin de spreads de crdito sugiere solvencia, el vector OGV plano y la tasa real del 1,77% impiden la expansin agresiva de renta variable. Los flujos priorizan la convexidad de materias primas (oro/cobre), compensando la degradacin del sentimiento cripto. Se requiere paciencia tctica hasta que la aceleracin del rgimen supere el umbral de 55. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
reports.ID: NETRALITAS STABIL DI TENGAH ROTASI ASET STRATEGIS. Skor GMS 48 mendikte postur netral saat neksus fiskal-moneter stabil dalam transisi Fase 2. Meskipun kompresi spread kredit menunjukkan solvensi tangguh, vektor OGV datar dan suku bunga riil 1,77% menghambat ekspansi ekuitas agresif. Aliran modal memprioritaskan konveksitas komoditas (emas/tembaga), mengimbangi degradasi sentimen kripto. Kesabaran taktis diperlukan hingga akselerasi rezim menembus ambang batas 55 secara definitif. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
reports.DE: STABILE NEUTRALITT BEI STRATEGISCHER SACHWERTEROTATION. Der GMS-Wert von 48 erzwingt eine neutrale Haltung, whrend sich der Fiskal-Monetr-Nexus in Phase 2 stabilisiert. Trotz Kreditspread-Kompression im HY-Sektor verhindern der flache OGV-Vektor und ein Realzins von 1,77 % eine aggressive Expansion. Kapitalflsse bevorzugen Rohstoff-Konvexitt (Gold/Kupfer) und neutralisieren die Degradierung des Krypto-Sentiments. Taktische Geduld ist geboten, bis die Regime-Beschleunigung die 55er-Schwelle durchbricht. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
reports.FR: NEUTRALIT STABLE SOUS ROTATION STRATGIQUE DES ACTIFS. Le GMS de 48 impose une posture neutre alors que le nexus fiscaux-montaire se stabilise en Phase 2. Bien que la compression des spreads de crdit signale une solvabilit rsiliente, le vecteur OGV plat et un taux d'intrt rel de 1,77 % limitent l'expansion agressive des actions. Les flux de capitaux privilgient la convexit des matires premires, compensant la dgradation du sentiment crypto. Une patience tactique s'impose jusqu' ce que l'acclration dpasse le seuil de 55. [ACTION: WAIT FOR PULLBACK]
